Seven other people, including a 6-year-old girl, were injured during the shooting. It is alleged that a group of men stormed the house and started shooting randomly. Police spokesperson Brigadier Novela Potelwa said five people died on the scene, seven were injured and taken to hospital and one person died shortly after arrival in hospital. “Provincial detectives are hard at work probing cases of murder and attempted murder. Police are urging anyone with information that could assist in expediting the investigation to contact the Crime Stop,” Potelwa said. – News24 . DM Please note you must be a Maverick Insider to comment. Sign up here or sign in if you are already an Insider.